{"tid":929811,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"華為CFO 係溫哥華比人拉左","createTime":"2018-12-06T00:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T01:50:48.000Z","uid":106998,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4c7091337628c4739aa002fe597c0411aa3fe2","tid":929811,"uid":106998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:13:26.000Z","msg":"加拿大報紙環球郵報（the Globe and Mail）引述加國司法部的聲明報導，加國已逮捕華為首席財務官孟晚舟，她因涉嫌違反美國對伊朗的貿易制裁而將被引渡到美國。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大應美國當局要求在溫哥華逮捕了孟晚舟。加國司法部聲明說：「孟晚舟於12月1日在溫哥華被捕。美國要求將她引渡，擬於周五舉行保釋聽證會。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-huawei-arrest-cfo-1.4934269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-huawei-arrest-cfo-1.4934269&d=FUNJkixV47%2Bc3WPZyQz53smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0e928fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-huawei-arrest-cfo-1.4934269</a>"},{"pid":"578d74beead1cc54349ab872b4c70ce24ef16d14","tid":929811,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e00cac4377b45aabf10885cfc42276c620e9b","tid":929811,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:26:16.000Z","msg":"保釋到實走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c88fdc86ab8d4db806910d3665c1905062fdae","tid":929811,"uid":19858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"保釋邊可能<br />\n何志平都走唔甩<br />\n你咁重要人質會俾你走佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486d0efda5e326cbafdb856c15ffe3974eae5b0c","tid":929811,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21c88fdc86ab8d4db806910d3665c1905062fdae","tid":929811,"uid":19858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c